[{"index":1,"title":"【随笔】等待","content":"&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;我喜欢在海边溜达,看风起云落,看海涛汹涌。我从那里，从远方，看到了我的未来。&nbsp;\r<br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;————题记\r<br>\r<br>\r<br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;感觉我好像一直在等待。\r<br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r<br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;等待一个人的出现，等待一棵花的开放，等待一本书的出版，等待一句话的感动。在我的生活里，&nbsp;我等待过很多东西，却唯独没有等待过我自己。\r<br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r<br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;等待我自己长大，等待我自己自信,等待我自己快乐，等待我自己幸福。等待我的一切一切，变得更好，让我有勇气对自己说：“你是最棒的！”\r<br>\r<br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;不过，没关系。因为，从今天开始，我要学会不再等待别人，我要等待的，是我自己。&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r<br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r<br>\u0018","author":"祭璃￠","author_link":"https://tieba.baidu.com/home/main?id=tb.1.c98790fc.0v-x0lStqklf5yaOgZBPlw&fr=pb","date":"2006-08-11 12:36","ip":null,"old_image":null,"user_sign_image":null},{"index":2,"title":"回复：【随笔】等待","content":"再次SF�","author":"浮云残雪泪","author_link":"https://tieba.baidu.com/home/main?id=tb.1.53277d52.MNH2a8Z8_ytAJWilnC8ykg&fr=pb","date":"2006-08-11 13:06","ip":null,"old_image":null,"user_sign_image":null},{"index":3,"title":"回复：【随笔】等待","content":"心碎了一地，该用什么去挽囬；明天的明天，又该怎样去度过…�","author":"祭璃￠","author_link":"https://tieba.baidu.com/home/main?id=tb.1.c98790fc.0v-x0lStqklf5yaOgZBPlw&fr=pb","date":"2006-08-11 13:06","ip":null,"old_image":null,"user_sign_image":null},{"index":4,"title":"回复：【随笔】等待","content":"云啊………�","author":"祭璃￠","author_link":"https://tieba.baidu.com/home/main?id=tb.1.c98790fc.0v-x0lStqklf5yaOgZBPlw&fr=pb","date":"2006-08-11 13:06","ip":null,"old_image":null,"user_sign_image":null},{"index":5,"title":"回复：【随笔】等待","content":"本来人生就是等待嘛……\n知道就可以……说这么多话根本没有意义……\n做自己想做的，让自己不枉此生9.OK�","author":"浮云残雪泪","author_link":"https://tieba.baidu.com/home/main?id=tb.1.53277d52.MNH2a8